{"id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0001", "text": "如果你想我哭 憑恐嚇就能夠", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 9, 5, 9, 5, 3, 0, 9, 4, 2, 0, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "gwo2", "nei5", "soeng2", "ngo5", "huk1", "pang4", "hung2", "haak3", "zau6", "nang4", "gau3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如果", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "想", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "哭", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "憑", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "恐嚇", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "就", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "能夠", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "不要離我太遠", "artists": ["鄧麗欣"], "lyricists": ["Cookies", "黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1312", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0002", "text": "而你其實不必 真的要走", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 0, 2, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ji4", "nei5", "kei4", "sat6", "bat1", "bit1", "zan1", "dik1", "jiu3", "zau2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "而", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "其實", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不必", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "真的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "走", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "不要離我太遠", "artists": ["鄧麗欣"], "lyricists": ["Cookies", "黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1312", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0003", "text": "除非我不夠好 毋需再做朋友", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 5, 3, 4, 9, 0, 3, 4, 2, 0, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ceoi4", "fei1", "ngo5", "bat1", "gau3", "hou2", "mou4", "seoi1", "zoi3", "zou6", "pang4", "jau5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "除非", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不夠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "毋需", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "朋友", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "不要離我太遠", "artists": ["鄧麗欣"], "lyricists": ["Cookies", "黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1312", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0004", "text": "而你情願孤單 都不接受", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 0, 2, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ji4", "nei5", "cing4", "jyun6", "gu1", "daan1", "dou1", "bat1", "zip3", "sau6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "而", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "情願", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "孤單", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "接受", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "不要離我太遠", "artists": ["鄧麗欣"], "lyricists": ["Cookies", "黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1312", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0005", "text": "要是我 先開口 很需要 你逗留", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 5, 3, 3, 9, 9, 3, 4, 5, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jiu3", "si6", "ngo5", "sin1", "hoi1", "hau2", "han2", "seoi1", "jiu3", "nei5", "dau6", "lau4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "要是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "先", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "開口", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "很", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "需要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "逗留", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "不要離我太遠", "artists": ["鄧麗欣"], "lyricists": ["Cookies", "黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1312", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0006", "text": "告白有用 還是根本沒有", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 5, 2, 0, 2, 3, 9, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["gou3", "baak6", "jau5", "jung6", "waan4", "si6", "gan1", "bun2", "mut6", "jau5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "告白", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有用", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "根本", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "不要離我太遠", "artists": ["鄧麗欣"], "lyricists": ["Cookies", "黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1312", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0007", "text": "求求你 保護我 可是個 更差理由", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 5, 9, 2, 5, 9, 2, 4, 3, 5, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["kau4", "kau4", "nei5", "bou2", "wu6", "ngo5", "ho2", "si6", "go3", "caa1", "lei5", "jau4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "求求", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "保護", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "更差", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "理由", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "不要離我太遠", "artists": ["鄧麗欣"], "lyricists": ["Cookies", "黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1312", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6YKT5Li95qyj_MTMxMg_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
